name: The OWL ZINGER LTD.
description:
GREENISSUE is proud to offer the OWL ZINGER LTD. (only 50 available) board benefiting the animals affected by the tragic oil spill in the Gulf of Mexico.

Treasured wildlife and wild places have been devastated by the BP oil spill. An estimated 186 million gallons have poured into the Gulf of Mexico impacting dolphins, brown pelicans, as well as threatened and endangered sea turtles. Some animals have been found dead. Others have been found dying or coated in the toxic oil that has polluted extensive areas of their habitat.

Yet the visible toll on wildlife is only the tip of the iceberg. The long term impacts of this tragedy have still not been fully realized. In fact, now that the leak has been capped, our work has really just begun (text taken from www.nwf.org)

GREENISSUE will donate $10.00 to the National Wildlife Federation’s Gulf Oil Spill Restoration Fund (www.nwf.org) for each OWL ZINGER LTD. board sold.

The OWLZINGERLTD.
7.5” wide 28.75” long with a 14” wheelbase.

description:

name: Haiti Relief Tee
description:
Every bit counts and we art trying to do our part here at GI. So we are offering up this tee with 100% of the profits going to help our brothers and sisters in Haiti. 

White only 
size M-XL

*Update- We would like to know how you would like us to put this money to use. When you make your purchase please give us your suggestion as to which agency (the Red Cross, Doctors without Boarders, etc.) you would like the money to go to. We will put all the suggestions together  and make the donation to the top 1 or 2 agencies that you choose. 

Thanks everyone for your support on this project. We have had many requests for the donations to go to The Red Cross www.redcross.org and World Concern www.worldconcern.org . 

Thanks to everyone who has purchased and donated through our program.

Sorry all Size Medium- SOLD OUT! 

GreenIssue

name: BONES A-Skate Benefit Wheels
description:
Prev
Next

A- SKATE BENEFIT
52mm x 31mm

Autism, like skateboarding, can be unpredictable and oftentimes unruly. We embrace the parts of autism that are hard to understand and give these kids an outlet that is free of rules or judgement, while allowing them to be social.
The Blue wheel represents Autism and our commitment to help create an outlet for kids who are affected by this disorder. Thank you for your support.

Diameter: 52mm
Width: 31mm

3 white wheels and 1 blue wheel
Hardness: 83B
Formula: STF

name: BONES BUSHINGS
description:
SOFT
Provide very easy turning, quick, smooth response and good centering. We recommend them for skaters who like their trucks loose, but not floppy, longboarders, and little skaters for whom a soft HardCore will feel like a medium or firm bushing.

Hardness: 81A


MEDIUM
Formulated for the majority of skaters who already have good control of their board and just want quick, positive response, centering and the control to skate anything or anywhere.

Hardness: 91A

HARD
Provide high resistance to turning throughout the entire turning range and ultra quick response.

Hardness: 96A
